@startuml Staff Management - Component Communication
title Staff Management: Create / Update / List / Toggle Status

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
top to bottom direction

actor "Owner" as Owner

package "API" {
  [StaffAccountController] as StaffController
}

package "Services" {
  [StaffAccountService] as StaffSvc
  [BranchService] as BranchSvc
}

package "Persistence" {
  [StaffAccountRepository] as StaffRepo
  [BranchRepository] as BranchRepo
  [UserRepository] as UserRepo
}

Owner --> StaffController : createStaffAccount\nupdateStaffAccount\ngetStaffAccountById\nsetStaffAccountStatus\ngetStaffByBranchPaginated

StaffController --> StaffSvc : createStaffAccount(request)\nupdateStaffAccount(dto)\ngetStaffAccountById(id)\nsetStaffAccountStatus(id)\ngetStaffAccountByBranchPaginated(page, size, branchId)

StaffSvc --> BranchSvc : findById(branchId)
StaffSvc --> StaffRepo : save\nfindById\nfindByBranch
StaffSvc --> UserRepo : findById (if linked user)

note bottom of StaffSvc
  createStaffAccount: assign branch, role (BRANCH_MANAGER / STAFF).
  setStaffAccountStatus: toggle ACTIVE ↔ INACTIVE.
  Assign branch manager: via Branch or Staff API.
end note

@enduml
